Cross-check against the production-side average above, **fixed at the 10% shift level** (independent methodology — full O-D skim × trip volume, not PMT/trips):

- **City Area**: weighted-average trip length changes by **-0.96 miles**.
- **Medium District**: weighted-average trip length changes by **-0.94 miles**.
- **Workshop Area**: weighted-average trip length changes by **-0.74 miles**.


